OL,3,CClaire Throssell calls for children to
OL,4,Chave more of a 'voice' over custody
OL,6,FA woman whose two sons were killed by
OL,7,Ftheir father in Penistone is taking
OL,8,Fpart in a fun run in their memory,
OL,9,Falmost ten years on from when they
OL,10,Fwere murdered.JClaire Throssell MBE,
OL,11,Fand two of her sons' friends, will
OL,12,Fparticipate in the two-kilometre run
OL,13,Faround the South Yorkshire village on
OL,14,FSunday 9 June at 10:30am.JHer two
OL,15,Fsons, 12-year-old Jack and 9-year-old
OL,16,FPaul, were murdered by her ex-husband
OL,17,FDarren Sykes in October 2014 in a
OL,18,Fhouse fire at their family home.JSykes
OL,19,Falso died in the blaze.JClaire was
OL,20,Fawarded an MBE in 2021 for her
OL,21,Fcampaigning on behalf of children
OL,22,Fsuffering domestic abuse.JShe is
OL,23,Fpetitioning the Government to
OL,24,Fintroduce legislation which gives
OL,25,Fchildren more of a say about which
OL,26,Fparent they spend time with if there
