OL,6,F"It gives them a voice."JSunday's fun
OL,7,Frun will raise money for Heads
OL,8,FTogether (Barnsley) Charitable Trust
OL,9,Fwhich was set up in Jack and Paul's
OL,10,Fmemory.JIt will be the seventh time
OL,11,FClaire has organised the annual fun
OL,12,Frun in Penistone which she hopes will
OL,13,Fhelp promote the legislation changes
OL,14,Fshe would like to see by taking her
OL,15,Fbeyond the 100,000 signature threshold
OL,16,Fwhich would mean her proposals could
OL,17,Fbe debated in Parliament.JSpeaking
OL,18,Fabout how she feels a decade on from
OL,19,Fthe death of Jack and Paul, Claire
OL,20,Ftold ITV News: "Whenever I walk into a
OL,21,Froom, it might be full of friends, it
OL,22,Fmight be full of family but it's the
OL,23,Floneliest place in the world because
OL,24,Fthe two faces, the two voices that I
OL,25,Fwant to see, are never there.J"They
OL,26,Fused to say wherever I was was home
